  "body": "### Description\r\n\r\nWhen creating new account, screen with available authentication methods should be shown: \r\n\r\n![authentication method](https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/23836/45511009-82190f00-b7a4-11e8-9d77-33cab17c079f.png)\r\n\r\n\r\n\"set up password\" leads to old-style password auth flow.\r\n\r\n\"set up status hardwallet\" shows following screen if NFC is ON:\r\n\r\n![hardwallet product screen 2x](https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/23836/45482645-4e63c800-b757-11e8-9a11-06083a8a73b3.png)\r\n\r\nAnd this screen when NFC is OFF:\r\n\r\n![error nfc is off](https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/23836/45482758-984cae00-b757-11e8-80c9-9bdbdbdf8bee.png)\r\n\r\n### Notes\r\n\r\nPlease refer to Figma Flows for screen stylings (they are not 100% precise now, but good enough to convert them to screens).\r\n\r\nFlows diagram: https://www.figma.com/file/UfQjpWl1hmRchHIyY3Wvu2nW/Hardwallet-light-flows\r\n\r\nNFC Library: https://github.com/whitedogg13/react-native-nfc-manager\r\n\r\n<blockquote><img src=\"https://s3-alpha.figma.com/thumbnails/0c5aa83e-f64a-44d2-9dd5-d49878fa5ac2\" width=\"48\" align=\"right\"><div><img src=\"https://static.figma.com/app/icon/1/favicon.svg\" height=\"14\"> Figma</div><div><strong><a href=\"https://www.figma.com/file/UfQjpWl1hmRchHIyY3Wvu2nW/Hardwallet-light-flows\">Figma</a></strong></div><div>Created with Figma</div></blockquote>\r\n<blockquote><img src=\"https://avatars1.githubusercontent.com/u/10307875?s=400&v=4\" width=\"48\" align=\"right\"><div><img src=\"https://assets-cdn.github.com/favicon.ico\" height=\"14\"> GitHub</div><div><strong><a href=\"https://github.com/whitedogg13/react-native-nfc-manager\">whitedogg13/react-native-nfc-manager</a></strong></div><div>React Native NFC module for both Android & iOS. Contribute to whitedogg13/react-native-nfc-manager development by creating an account on GitHub.</div></blockquote>",
